    <item>
      <title>日经新闻称日产撤回本田整合计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/nissan-withdraws-honda-integration-plan-nikkei-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《日经新闻》报道，日产汽车公司将退出与本田汽车公司的交易，以合并两个品牌并重获全球竞争力。东京证券交易所因该报道暂停了日产股票的交易。彭博社的 Danny Lee 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-05/nissan-withdraws-honda-integration-plan-nikkei-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 07:37:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 CATL 计划在未来几周申请香港上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/catl-is-said-to-eye-filing-for-hong-kong-listing-in-coming-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，宁德时代新能源科技股份有限公司正考虑最早于本月或三月初提交香港上市申请。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/catl-is-said-to-eye-filing-for-hong-kong-listing-in-coming-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 07:37:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维斯塔斯将以更强劲的收益回报投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/vestas-to-return-profit-to-investors-with-stronger-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维斯塔斯风力发电系统公司 (Vestas Wind Systems A/S) 宣布回购 1 亿欧元（1.04 亿美元）的股票，并恢复向投资者派发股息，此前该公司因成本飙升导致巨额亏损，多年来一直努力提高价格，如今开始收获成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/vestas-to-return-profit-to-investors-with-stronger-earnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 07:10:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葛兰素史克计划回购 20 亿英镑股票，提升长期前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gsk-announces-2-billion-share-buyback-as-profit-beats-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葛兰素史克公司 (GSK Plc) 计划回购 20 亿英镑（25 亿美元）的股票，因为市场对药物研发渠道的乐观情绪提高了其长期增长前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gsk-announces-2-billion-share-buyback-as-profit-beats-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 07:09:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TotalEnergies 通过提高股息和维持回购来摆脱利润下滑的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/totalenergies-shrugs-off-weaker-profits-by-lifting-dividend-keeping-buybacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道达尔能源公司 (TotalEnergies SE) 提高了股息，并保持了股票回购步伐，不受油价下跌和炼油利润率下降导致的第四季度盈利下降的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/totalenergies-shrugs-off-weaker-profits-by-lifting-dividend-keeping-buybacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 07:02:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>野村证券利润因交易繁荣和成本削减而超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/nomura-profit-beats-estimates-led-by-equities-and-bond-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村控股公司 (Nomura Holdings Inc.) 的利润增幅超过分析师的预期，因为这家日本最大的经纪公司从强劲的交易和投资银行业务中获益，并在削减成本方面取得了进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/nomura-profit-beats-estimates-led-by-equities-and-bond-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 06:38:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度交易员重写策略以转向波动性更大的卢比</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/new-reserve-bank-of-india-governor-shakes-up-traders-playbook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙克提坎塔·达斯担任印度央行行长最后两年，卢比汇率坚挺，流动性减少，利率居高不下。桑杰·马洛特拉似乎将打破这一模式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/new-reserve-bank-of-india-governor-shakes-up-traders-playbook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东京今年首支股票上市首日交易量飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/tokyo-s-first-ipo-this-year-bets-on-succession-in-manufacturing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[下一代技术集团有限公司 (Next Generation Technology Group Inc.) 是今年在东京证券交易所上市的首家公司，其股价在交易首日上涨，提振了人们对日本股票一级市场人气可能改善的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/tokyo-s-first-ipo-this-year-bets-on-succession-in-manufacturing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 23:13:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国多年来最热门的 IPO 首次公开募股 (IPO) 首日表现不佳，因 IPO 热潮降温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/lg-cns-set-to-debut-after-south-korea-s-biggest-ipo-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LG CNS Co. 首次公开募股 (IPO) 规模为 1.2 万亿韩元（8.21 亿美元），在首尔交易日首日股价下跌，成为韩国两年多以来规模最大的新股上市交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/lg-cns-set-to-debut-after-south-korea-s-biggest-ipo-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
